{"tid":1675174,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"想讀動畫 遊戲藝術設計果類 應該去台灣定留喺香港讀？","createTime":"2019-10-25T16:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T16:33:22.000Z","uid":312829,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"88ec1002e376f15d6d955123cf4ea0358750c999","tid":1675174,"uid":312829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T16:32:46.000Z","msg":"香港有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">city creative media</span></span>  <br />\n聽人講話其實係入去識人同靠自學<br />\n又話咩animation elective 爭幾年都可能爭唔到讀<br />\n<br />\n台灣有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">台藝大多媒體動畫藝術學系</span></span> or <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">北藝大動畫學系</span></span><br />\n四年大學生涯都係專攻動畫 遊戲設計果類 係必修<br />\n但係聽人講又話台灣讀完認受性唔高 出嚟搵唔到工<br />\n但係喺香港讀藝術搞藝術又好似嘥鬼氣<br />\n<br />\n有冇有經驗嘅巴打絲打指點下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗到頭髮都甩晒"},{"pid":"7f3d43896ab2ac163aa69aad40f3670a1b8200b6","tid":1675174,"uid":44073,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T16:34:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"422e6946bb3c7dd42d03365cc44595f62b1c2e6a","tid":1675174,"uid":312829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f3d43896ab2ac163aa69aad40f3670a1b8200b6","tid":1675174,"uid":44073,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T16:34:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T16:34:35.000Z","msg":"你指cm?"},{"pid":"f06d9da1e494809c73db8e9fd1f71a57725251ef","tid":1675174,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T16:35:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99fd2e7db63d083781b913191030c7623a6e5b6c","tid":1675174,"uid":312829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"